{"id":199,"date":"2021-07-22T10:01:34","date_gmt":"2021-07-22T17:01:34","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/?page_id=199"},"modified":"2024-08-06T23:55:04","modified_gmt":"2024-08-07T05:55:04","slug":"safety","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/safety\/","title":{"rendered":"Safety"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<div class=\"wp-block-cover is-style-hero-inside\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-cover__background has-background-dim-30 has-background-dim\"><\/span><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1365\" class=\"wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-1805\" alt=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Hero-Image-Option1-2.jpg\" style=\"object-position:29% 48%\" data-object-fit=\"cover\" data-object-position=\"29% 48%\" srcset=\"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Hero-Image-Option1-2.jpg 2048w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Hero-Image-Option1-2-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Hero-Image-Option1-2-1600x1066.jpg 1600w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Hero-Image-Option1-2-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Hero-Image-Option1-2-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\" \/><div class=\"wp-block-cover__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-cover-is-layout-flow\">\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Safety is life<sub>With safety at our core, we exhibit exemplary performance and commit to the well-being of our people&nbsp;<\/sub><\/h1>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-layout-flex wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link wp-element-button\" href=\"#learn-more\">Learn More <img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-316\" style=\"width: NaNpx;\" src=\"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/arrow-down.svg\" alt=\"\"><\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-style-block-section\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-cover is-style-right-image-content\" id=\"learn-more\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-cover__background has-background-dim\"><\/span><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1365\" class=\"wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-1806\" alt=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Safety-Section1-MPRP-2.jpg\" data-object-fit=\"cover\" srcset=\"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Safety-Section1-MPRP-2.jpg 2048w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Safety-Section1-MPRP-2-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Safety-Section1-MPRP-2-1600x1066.jpg 1600w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Safety-Section1-MPRP-2-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/Safety-Section1-MPRP-2-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px\" \/><div class=\"wp-block-cover__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-cover-is-layout-flow\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading is-style-has-underline has-black-color has-text-color\">Our safety pillars set the foundation for our success<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Safety is a constant state of mind, ingrained into our attitudes, values, goals, and behaviors because simply having the best training, tools, equipment, processes, and procedures is not enough to keep us safe. Our behavioral commitment to safety and strong culture is built upon tenacious dedication from management, employee involvement, excellent training programs, industry involvement, and a constant focus on innovation and improvement.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Our dedication and efforts result in outstanding safety performance and our industry-leading reputation as a top specialty electrical contractor.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-style-block-section has-myrgroup-gray-dark-background-color has-background\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-cover is-style-left-image-content\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-cover__background has-background-dim\"><\/span><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" class=\"wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-2539\" alt=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/IMG_4470-Edit-scaled.jpg\" style=\"object-position:80% 51%\" data-object-fit=\"cover\" data-object-position=\"80% 51%\" srcset=\"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/IMG_4470-Edit-scaled.jpg 2560w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/IMG_4470-Edit-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/IMG_4470-Edit-1600x1067.jpg 1600w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/IMG_4470-Edit-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/IMG_4470-Edit-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/IMG_4470-Edit-2048x1365.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><div class=\"wp-block-cover__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-cover-is-layout-flow\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading is-style-has-underline\">High Degree of Employee Involvement<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>We prioritize training and developing our employees and equipping them with the right tools, equipment, resources, and knowledge to make informed decisions. Through extensive training programs that focus on tactical skills and human behavior, we empower our people to take responsibility for their actions and for those around them. This personal dedication and unrelenting commitment to safety lead to improved performance, increased engagement, reduced turnover, and enhanced morale. Our employees are crucial to our safety culture, and we strive to ensure everyone returns home safe at the end of each day.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>As an active partner with industry agencies, trade partners, and clients, we continuously look for innovative ways to improve our safety programs and implement best practices to improve worker safety. In the end, we will never compromise when safety is on the line.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-style-block-section\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-cover is-style-right-image-content\" id=\"learn-more\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-cover__background has-background-dim\"><\/span><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1600\" class=\"wp-block-cover__image-background wp-image-8177\" alt=\"\" src=\"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/LEM-Decatur-VPP-STAR-Status-Flag-1-scaled.jpg\" style=\"object-position:49% 32%\" data-object-fit=\"cover\" data-object-position=\"49% 32%\" srcset=\"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/LEM-Decatur-VPP-STAR-Status-Flag-1-scaled.jpg 2560w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/LEM-Decatur-VPP-STAR-Status-Flag-1-1024x640.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/LEM-Decatur-VPP-STAR-Status-Flag-1-1600x1000.jpg 1600w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/LEM-Decatur-VPP-STAR-Status-Flag-1-768x480.jpg 768w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/LEM-Decatur-VPP-STAR-Status-Flag-1-1536x960.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/LEM-Decatur-VPP-STAR-Status-Flag-1-2048x1280.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><div class=\"wp-block-cover__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-cover-is-layout-flow\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading is-style-has-underline has-black-color has-text-color\">Proud OSHA VPP STAR Status Members<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>OSHA\u2019s Voluntary Protection Program (VPP) promotes effective worksite-based safety and health with management, labor, and OSHA establishing cooperative relationships at workplaces that have implemented a comprehensive safety and health management system. Approval into VPP is OSHA\u2019s official recognition of the outstanding efforts of employers and employees who have achieved exemplary occupational safety and health.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>MYR Group has multiple districts that have earned VPP STAR status, the organization\u2019s highest grade, stringently reserved for organizations that develop and implement continuous improvement in workplace safety and health management. These programs must result in injury and illness rates below the national averages for their industries. All organizations that reach the top tier of the VPP program must undergo three-year audits, rigorous onsite evaluations, and an ongoing renewal process.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Consistent resources must be dedicated to continue meeting VPP\u2019s ever-changing criteria, which is additionally difficult while maintaining a mobile workforce. We continually push forward to remain at the forefront of health and safety and consistently renew our districts as VPP Program, as well as add more districts across the company into this prestigious program through MERIT and STAR status.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-layout-flex wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link wp-element-button\" href=\"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/news\/sturgeon-electrics-sustained-osha-vpp-star-status-a-testament-to-leadership-commitment\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">LEARN MORE<\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-style-block-section safety-awards-section\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center has-black-color has-text-color\"><sup>Industry Recognition<\/sup>Awards For Safety &amp; Innovation<\/h2>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-myrgroup-awards-carousel\">\r\n\r\n<div class=\"carousel\">\r\n<div class=\"slide\">\r\n  <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"320\" height=\"193\" src=\"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/awards-voluntary-protection-programs.jpg\" class=\"attachment-medium size-medium\" alt=\"\" \/><\/div>\r\n<div class=\"slide\">\r\n  <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"500\" height=\"273\" src=\"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/Neca_logo.jpg\" class=\"attachment-medium size-medium\" alt=\"\" \/><\/div>\r\n<div class=\"slide\">\r\n  <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"741\" height=\"416\" src=\"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/AGCC-Mountain-Only.png\" class=\"attachment-medium size-medium\" alt=\"Associated General Contractors of Colorado logo\" \/><\/div>\r\n<div class=\"slide\">\r\n  <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"846\" height=\"516\" src=\"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/ASP-Logo.jpg\" class=\"attachment-medium size-medium\" alt=\"American Society of Safety Professionals logo\" srcset=\"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/ASP-Logo.jpg 846w, https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/ASP-Logo-768x468.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 846px) 100vw, 846px\" \/><\/div>\r\n\r\n<\/div>\r\n\r\n<\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-style-block-section footer-call-to-action\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns has-myrgroup-blue-background-color has-background is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-1 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:66.66%\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-white-color has-text-color\">See our safety program in action<\/h2>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:33.33%\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-layout-flex wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link wp-element-button\" href=\"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/news\/categories\/safety\/\">Industry recognition<\/a><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Industry RecognitionAwards For Safety &amp; Innovation See our safety program in action<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":20,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-199","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/199"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=199"}],"version-history":[{"count":31,"href":"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/199\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":9026,"href":"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/199\/revisions\/9026"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/myrgroup.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=199"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}